  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 200°C (392°F).",
    "Season chicken with salt and pepper. Drizzle olive oil over both sides.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together brown sugar, garlic, butter and a pinch of black pepper.",
    "Place chicken on a baking sheet and pour the mixture evenly onto each piece.",
    "Roast in the preheated oven for 25 minutes or until golden brown and cooked through.",
    "Meanwhile, heat apricot preserves with a little bit of water in a small saucepan. Reduce to thicken slightly.",
    "Remove chicken from oven and drizzle with thickened apricot glaze. Serve immediately.",
    "Enjoy your raw-friendly British dish!"
